00:03:37.720 --> 00:03:42.650
So first, how far has YouTube
gotten in the last few years?

00:03:42.650 --> 00:03:47.160
YouTube is now watched by most
people on the web each month.

00:03:47.160 --> 00:03:50.910
Whether they are coming the
directly to the site, or they

00:03:50.910 --> 00:03:53.610
watch our embedded player, which
is on lots of sites and

00:03:53.610 --> 00:03:58.570
blogs throughout the web, lots
and lots of people consume

00:03:58.570 --> 00:03:59.400
online video.

00:03:59.400 --> 00:04:00.820
