realize is that YouTube is now

00:05:06.860 --> 00:05:08.950
far more than a website.

00:05:08.950 --> 00:05:13.860
We're on most of the phones out
there, over 350 million,

00:05:13.860 --> 00:05:16.840
pre-installed on
a lot of them.

00:05:16.840 --> 00:05:20.500
And mobile viewing of
the site is growing

00:05:20.500 --> 00:05:21.620
by leaps and bounds.

00:05:21.620 --> 00:05:23.990
It's tripled in just
the last year.

00:05:23.990 --> 00:05:27.980
And I think it's clearly a
question of when, not if,

00:05:27.980 --> 00:05:29.700
mobile viewing of YouTube
videos will

00:05:29.700 --> 00:05:31.980
surpass desktop viewing.

00:05:31.980 --> 00:05:35.630
So if you take a step back,
and you think about people

00:05:35.630 --> 00:05:37.850
