watch the video.

00:39:00.080 --> 00:39:02.210
This was interesting for
a couple reasons.

00:39:02.210 --> 00:39:04.510
The first is, as a video
creator, you can see what's

00:39:04.510 --> 00:39:06.120
engaging about the video.

00:39:06.120 --> 00:39:08.950
And you can continually hone
your craft and figure out how

00:39:08.950 --> 00:39:11.450
to make better videos
going forward.

00:39:11.450 --> 00:39:14.200
But you can also put different
products and features

00:39:14.200 --> 00:39:17.600
throughout your video and use
this, as a proxy, to see what

00:39:17.600 --> 00:39:18.960
