AJ CRANE: Go ahead.

00:45:16.559 --> 00:45:18.451
AUDIENCE: [INAUDIBLE]

00:45:18.451 --> 00:45:21.380
DROR SHIMSHOWITZ: Oh sorry, if
you could, please, go to the

00:45:21.380 --> 00:45:24.740
mic to ask your question, which
