Thanks.

00:50:46.372 --> 00:50:50.050
AUDIENCE: What's, like, a good
best practice for handling

00:50:50.050 --> 00:50:52.611
negative comments?

00:50:52.611 --> 00:50:54.960
DROR SHIMSHOWITZ: Yeah, comments
are kind of the Wild

00:50:54.960 --> 00:50:58.270
West of video.

00:50:58.270 --> 00:51:00.930
One approach is you can
turn off comments, and

00:51:00.930 --> 00:51:02.450
some brands do that.

00:51:02.450 --> 00:51:04.950
We don't encourage that, because
it kind of cuts off

00:51:04.950 --> 00:51:06.880
the community.

00:51:06.880 --> 00:51:09.290
And we think that the best
comments will rise to the top,

00:51:09.290 --> 00:51:11.050
in the top comments section.

00:51:11.050 --> 00:51:12.550
We're also working on
some improvements to

00:51:12.550 --> 00:51:14.650
the comments system.

00:51:14.650 --> 00:51:16.990
So, hopefully, we'll have
an update on that in

00:51:16.990 --> 00:51:18.240
the next few months.

00:51:21.170 --> 00:51:24.130
AUDIENCE: I have a question on
best practices to limit the

00:51:24.130 --> 00:51:27.240
visibility of videos, if you
have IP or something that

00:51:27.240 --> 00:51:30.660
you're posting, you guys
thinking about doing,

00:51:30.660 --> 00:51:33.420
basically, something similar to
circles, or do you have any

00:51:33.420 --> 00:51:37.960
other ideas for controlling
IP and videos?

00:51:37.960 --> 00:51:42.200
DROR SHIMSHOWITZ: Yes, so
currently, we have three

00:51:42.200 --> 00:51:43.770
privacy states for
YouTube video.

00:51:43.770 --> 00:51:46.640
You can make it private, which
means you can specify a

00:51:46.640 --> 00:51:48.190
limited number of people
to watch it.

00:51:48.190 --> 00:51:49.880
You actually name them.

00:51:49.880 --> 00:51:51.920
You can make it public, and
that's the other extreme.

00:51:51.920 --> 00:51:54.380
And then we also have unlisted,
where only people

00:51:54.380 --> 00:51:57.540
with the link will discover
the video.

00:51:57.540 --> 00:51:59.630
If anyone gets the link, they
can watch it, but it's

00:51:59.630 --> 00:52:01.710
security by obscurity.

00:52:01.710 --> 00:52:06.140
We're also working on some
additional forms of sharing.

00:52:06.140 --> 00:52:07.390
So stay tuned on that as well.

