We also have a live
streaming product.

00:52:33.070 --> 00:52:34.500
But right now, that's available

00:52:34.500 --> 00:52:35.760
to higher-end partners.

00:52:35.760 --> 00:52:39.120
There's a lot of setup cost
involved in that, and it's not

00:52:39.120 --> 00:52:40.810
yet a self-serve offering.

